1
00:00:05,271 --> 00:00:06,872
Hei Yan and him are livestreaming.

2
00:00:06,873 --> 00:00:08,307
My cousin wandered
into the shot like an idiot.

3
00:00:08,308 --> 00:00:10,310
Luckily, we played it off as a brand thing.

4
00:00:11,378 --> 00:00:13,747
Time to get up and eat.

5
00:00:14,114 --> 00:00:14,914
Why did it have to be...

6
00:00:14,914 --> 00:00:15,749
from this specific place?

7
00:00:15,750 --> 00:00:17,070
I stood in line forever for this!

8
00:00:17,784 --> 00:00:19,586
It all tastes the same anyway, doesn't it?

9
00:00:26,059 --> 00:00:27,160
Oh, really?

10
00:00:29,329 --> 00:00:31,564
Who was it that got drunk and said,

11
00:00:32,232 --> 00:00:33,832
"You used to take care of me,"

12
00:00:33,833 --> 00:00:36,302
"so now I'll take care of you"?

13
00:00:37,837 --> 00:00:38,937
Typical.

14
00:00:38,938 --> 00:00:40,139
A man's word...

15
00:00:40,140 --> 00:00:41,207
is nothing but a lie.

16
00:00:42,642 --> 00:00:43,710
That's not true!

17
00:00:47,881 --> 00:00:49,749
I'm letting you stay at my place, aren't I?

18
00:00:50,083 --> 00:00:51,523
You could've stayed at my place too.

19
00:00:52,685 --> 00:00:54,454
You mean in that tiny office of yours?

20
00:00:55,622 --> 00:00:57,123
We have to make it look real.

21
00:00:59,692 --> 00:01:00,794
Make what look real?

22
00:01:03,830 --> 00:01:05,899
Our relationship.

23
00:01:07,500 --> 00:01:09,035
I have a spare room.

24
00:01:10,170 --> 00:01:11,170
For what?

25
00:01:11,304 --> 00:01:12,372
To gather dust?

26
00:01:13,006 --> 00:01:14,107
Wanna keep me there?

27
00:01:44,571 --> 00:01:45,805
You want more already?

28
00:01:46,873 --> 00:01:47,807
Just eat your breakfast.

29
00:01:47,807 --> 00:01:48,807
No.

30
00:01:51,511 --> 00:01:54,013
I'm not ready for breakfast yet.

31
00:01:56,983 --> 00:01:57,983
Not yet?

32
00:01:58,017 --> 00:01:59,652
Not ready for breakfast, huh?

33
00:02:00,286 --> 00:02:01,286
Not yet...
